# Description
Enforce Next.js, TypeScript, functional React, and SEO best practices across the Charter Aviation Platform codebase.

# Applies to
src/**/*.{ts,tsx,js,jsx}
lib/**/*.{ts,tsx}
components/**/*.{ts,tsx}
pages/**/*.{ts,tsx}

